    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, with a deep shine and no visible imperfections, while the interior remains in 'like-new' state with no signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, and we have a complete service history documenting its care. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
