      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely gorgeous shape, looking just as stunning as the day it left the showroom. Every time I get behind the wheel, it still puts a massive smile on my face. It\u2019s been kept tucked away in a garage and treated with nothing but the best care. If you're looking for a ride that's been truly cherished and maintained to the highest standard, you've found it. Come by, let's chat cars, and you can see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
