    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Reluctantly parting with this absolute surgical instrument of a machine. This Evo X isn't just a car; it's a masterclass in kinetic management. We\u2019re talking a fully optimized 4B11T power plant with a precision-mapped twin-scroll turbocharger that delivers linear boost across the entire rev range. The Super All-Wheel Control (S-AWC) system has been meticulously calibrated for zero-latency torque distribution, ensuring peak lateral grip and composure through the apex. Suspension geometry is dialed in via high-frequency damping adjustment, providing a road-feel that is communicative yet never harsh. The SST dual-clutch transmission executes lightning-fast, rev-matched downshifts that would make a sequential box blush. Every fluid has been flushed and replaced with high-temp synthetics ahead of schedule. This is a turnkey, zero-compromise build for the discerning driver who values mechanical integrity over everything else.",
